{"tid":2143771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你想贏翻香港…入黎","createTime":"2020-08-07T09:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T18:21:34.000Z","uid":365231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9c69bac3bedaecdd47ff47650ee76bba7c7cf688","tid":2143771,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:35:22.000Z","msg":"香港宜家根本唔可以係體制內抗爭<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w1gHN6_RRSk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw1gHN6_RRSk&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=3f3aac3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w1gHN6_RRSk</a>[/url] <br />\n我自己覺得呢班人其實講得唔錯，搞類似波蘭流亡政府、法國抵抗運動等等。其實有無冧過搞香港抵抗運動呢?<br />\n而抵抗運動既唔係一班人係國外打飛機自hi，話齋搞流亡議會，打飛機要復國等等。<br />\n係要係海外搞屬於香港人既軍隊，要同英美加澳唔同國家搞既嘢，要佢哋幫手係海外訓練香港人成為軍隊。<br />\n<br />\n第一步要說服當地議會協助建立香港人既武裝力量<br />\n第二步要可能會同英美deal將來勝利既利益<br />\n第三步就要招人翻去練兵<br />\n最後一步就係等光復香港，睇幾時美向中宣戰就可以贏翻香港。<br />\n<br />\n※純學術討論※<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543dabe3e65cf11c789e2d37e64cf85ae09e50d4","tid":2143771,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:45:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"278ce126f685a7f62cc90d6016c9a3e5e0c5b380","tid":2143771,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:47:57.000Z","msg":"p牌仔推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a7bbe55503b4b03c6a86b87380b4ecc86fc475","tid":2143771,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"推&frac12;"},{"pid":"ba10219c4f7a946887511bac74cc55592043d2e9","tid":2143771,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:48:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35534390366d562fefae34aa92f2cfc83dbc9161","tid":2143771,"uid":365231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0594da1962079913bb0c7e34221fc421a61aae31","tid":2143771,"uid":365231,"